{"tid":417361,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【一裁再裁】思科再裁員 矽谷總部減310個職位","createTime":"2017-09-28T14:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T16:43:44.000Z","uid":44460,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c59c8228132da6e94030f8544eb6148f2dbaac3f","tid":417361,"uid":44460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"美國科技大廠思科（Cisco）周二證實將裁掉位於加州矽谷聖何塞總部的其中310個職位，這波裁員預計將從10月10日開始。<br />\n<br />\n思科在提交給州政府、由該公司法務長簽署的員工調整和再培訓通知（Worker Adjustment and Retraining Notification，WARN)）中公開裁員計劃，同時表明此次將會是永久性裁員。<br />\n<br />\n根據通知，裁員將由10月10日開始並持續至10月23日。當地傳媒報道，思科周二發表聲明表示，「我們定期進行業務評估，並將持續進行必要的改變，以有效地管理我們的投資組合，為我們的消費者和股東帶來最大的價值。因此，這可能代表重新調整某些領域，方便我們投資其他方面。」<br />\n<br />\n被裁掉的職位<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大部份是工程、軟件和技術職位，少部份為行政、管理和後勤</span></span>。思科在今年5月曾公佈會在聖何塞裁減250個職位，在全球總共減去1,100個職位。<br />\n<br />\n《聖何塞信使報》/《蘋果》資料室<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57266227&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57266227%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170928&d=wBeSCwnTTd5wjbNQPqXIAL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8b986215\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57266227%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170928&h=6163a863\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57266227&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170928</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做IT 死路一條, 個正苦仲叫人讀IT, 咁嚟害鳩人地屋企"},{"pid":"61466ade069af6d9d3b5634d014dfd9b77989a67","tid":417361,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8648a3bbba8a055834413179fa3c77bc78069684","tid":417361,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"356fb67a529fc6f5f0b599de64bbdfc449ba028d","tid":417361,"uid":44460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國it 都做唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能比華為打到仆街"},{"pid":"175a90ab1eb8ac4238ba424cc9730d2d60278039","tid":417361,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:20:37.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"0488ab7a38729322855f5192a12f173ec5c43e36","tid":417361,"uid":96465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:43:44.000Z","msg":"Cisco 套野根本就過時"}]}